## Animation Best Practices

### Use `viewport: { once: true }` for scroll animations
```typescript
// Prevents re-triggering on scroll back
viewport: { once: true }
```

### Group animations with parent hover
```tsx
<div className="group">
  <img className="group-hover:scale-105" />
  <div className="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
    Overlay
  </div>
</div>
```

### Stagger delays for multiple elements
```tsx
<motion.div transition={{ delay: 0 }}>First</motion.div>
<motion.div transition={{ delay: 0.2 }}>Second</motion.div>
<motion.div transition={{ delay: 0.4 }}>Third</motion.div>
```

### Ease functions
```typescript
ease: "easeOut"      // Smooth deceleration
ease: "easeInOut"    // Smooth both ways
ease: [0.4, 0, 0.2, 1]  // Custom cubic-bezier
```

## Performance Tips
1. Use `transform` and `opacity` for smooth animations (GPU accelerated)
2. Avoid animating `width`, `height`, `margin`, `padding`
3. Use `will-change` sparingly
4. Set `viewport: { once: true }` to prevent re-renders
